title: I Am Talent Pt. I with Chris Black
description:
BAH GAWD! THAT’S CHRIS BLACK’S MUSIC! The people’s champ returns to The Only Podcast That Matters™ to chop it up with the boys and lob a grip of his patented nuclear takes. From riding and dying for Chrome Hearts and his front line Fashion Month review, to what he actually does for a living and his Oscar futures, strap tf in for a jam-packed rollercoaster ride of clout. Plus, welcome to a new era of TF Wet™ sound production for your earholes courtesy of the one and only Chef Jam Recordings.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
